* '''降冰片基阳离子的[[溶解|溶解]]'''：为什么[[降冰片烷|降冰片基]]阳离子这么稳定？是因为它的对称性吗？如果是这样，又是为什么？这个问题很大程度上取决于降冰片基阳离子的不可替代性，这是其他[[碳正离子|碳正离子]]无法替代的<ref>{{cite journal|author=[[Saul_Winstein|Saul Winstein]] and D. S. Trifan|title=The structure of the bicyclo[2,2,1]2-heptyl (norbornyl) carbonium ion|year=1949|journal=[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]|volume=71|issue=8|pages=2953–2953|doi=10.1021/ja01176a536}}</ref>。参见[[非经典碳正离子|非经典碳正离子]]。
* '''[[水上反应|水上反应]]'''：为什么一些有机反应在水相和有机相的界面上会加快反应速率<ref>{{cite journal|pmid=15844112|year=2005|last1=Narayan|first1=S|last2=Muldoon|first2=J|last3=Finn|first3=MG|last4=Fokin|first4=VV|last5=Kolb|first5=HC|last6=Sharpless|first6=KB|title="On water": Unique reactivity of organic compounds in aqueous suspension|volume=44|issue=21|pages=3275–9|doi=10.1002/anie.200462883|journal=Angewandte Chemie (International ed. in English)}}</ref>？
* [[乙烷|乙烷]]中'''[[烷烃立体化学|键旋转障碍]]'''的本质原因究竟是[[空间位阻|空间位阻]]<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1002/anie.200350947|title=The Case for Steric Repulsion Causing the Staggered Conformation of Ethane|year=2003|last1=Bickelhaupt|first1=F. Matthias|last2=Baerends|first2=Evert Jan|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|volume=42|issue=35|pages=4183}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1002/anie.200352931|title=The Magnitude of Hyperconjugation in Ethane: A Perspective from Ab Initio Valence Bond Theory|year=2004|last1=Mo|first1=Yirong|last2=Wu|first2=Wei|last3=Song|first3=Lingchun|last4=Lin|first4=Menghai|last5=Zhang|first5=Qianer|last6=Gao|first6=Jiali|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|volume=43|issue=15|pages=1986}}</ref>还是[[超共轭效应|超共轭效应]]<ref name="goodman">{{cite journal | author = Pophristic, V.; Goodman, L. | journal = [[Nature_(journal)|Nature]] | doi = 10.1038/35079036 | year = 2001 | volume = 411 | pages = 565–8 | pmid = 11385566 | title = Hyperconjugation not steric repulsion leads to the staggered structure of ethane. | issue = 6837}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=周公度|title=导致乙烷的交叉型构象是超共轭作用而不是空间阻碍|journal=大学化学|volume=16|issue=5|pages=P51-52|accessdate=2012-01-16|date=2001年10月}}</ref>？ 
* '''[[邻位效应|邻位效应]]'''的本质原因是什么？亲核中心的邻位上有高[[电负性|电负性]]原子和一对或多对[[孤对电子|孤对电子]]时，[[亲核试剂|亲核试剂]]反应活性特别高<ref>{{cite journal|author=Ruediger, G. & Kichatinov, L. L.|title=Alpha-effect and alpha-quenching|journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics (ISSN 0004-6361)|year=1993|issue=269|pages=P581-588|accessdate=2012-01-16}}</ref>。
